{"id":132,"parent_id":121,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":132,"title":"Numbers 11","subtitle":"","short_title":"Num.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 11"],[".studySummary",["i","Fire from the Lord consumes the rebels in Israel—Israel murmurs and lusts for meat instead of manna—Moses complains that he cannot bear the burden alone—He is commanded to choose seventy elders to assist him—The Lord promises meat until it becomes loathsome to the Israelites—The seventy elders are chosen, they prophesy, the Lord comes down, and Eldad and Medad prophesy in the camp—Israel is provided with quail—The people lust, a great plague follows, and many die."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.1","order":"02.05.011.12036"},["b","1"],"And",["i","when"],"the people",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"complained"],", it displeased the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],": and the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"heard",["i","it;"],"and his anger was kindled; and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"fire"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"burnt among them, and consumed",["i","them that were"],"in the uttermost parts of the camp."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.2","order":"02.05.011.12037"},["b","2"],"And the people cried unto Moses; and when Moses prayed unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", the fire was quenched."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.3","order":"02.05.011.12038"},["b","3"],"And he called the name of the place Taberah: because the fire of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"burnt among them."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.4","order":"02.05.011.12039"},["b","4"],"¶And the mixed multitude that",["i","was"],"among them fell a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"lusting"],": and the children of Israel also wept again, and said, Who shall give us flesh to eat?"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.5","order":"02.05.011.12040"},["b","5"],"We remember the fish, which we did eat in Egypt freely; the cucumbers, and the melons, and the leeks, and the onions, and the garlick:"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.6","order":"02.05.011.12041"},["b","6"],"But now our soul",["i","is"],"dried away:",["i","there is"],"nothing at all, beside this manna,",["i","before"],"our eyes."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.7","order":"02.05.011.12042"},["b","7"],"And the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"manna"],["i","was"],"as",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"coriander"],"seed, and the colour thereof as the colour of bdellium."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.8","order":"02.05.011.12043"},["b","8"],["i","And"],"the people went about, and gathered",["i","it,"],"and ground",["i","it"],"in mills, or beat",["i","it"],"in a mortar, and baked",["i","it"],"in pans, and made cakes of it: and the taste of it was as the taste of fresh oil."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.9","order":"02.05.011.12044"},["b","9"],"And when the dew fell upon the camp in the night, the manna fell",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"upon it"],"."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.10","order":"02.05.011.12045"},["b","10"],"¶Then Moses heard the people weep throughout their families, every man in the door of his tent: and the anger of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"was kindled greatly; Moses also was displeased."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.11","order":"02.05.011.12046"},["b","11"],"And Moses said unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", Wherefore hast thou afflicted thy servant? and wherefore have I not found favour in thy sight, that thou layest the burden of all this people upon me?"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.12","order":"02.05.011.12047"},["b","12"],"Have I conceived all this people? have I begotten them, that thou shouldest say unto me, Carry them in thy bosom, as a nursing father beareth the sucking child, unto the land which thou swarest unto their fathers?"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.13","order":"02.05.011.12048"},["b","13"],"Whence should I have flesh to give unto all this people? for they weep unto me, saying, Give us flesh, that we may eat."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.14","order":"02.05.011.12049"},["b","14"],"I am not able to bear all this people alone, because",["i","it is"],"too",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"heavy"],"for me."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.15","order":"02.05.011.12050"},["b","15"],"And if thou deal thus with me, kill me, I pray thee,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"out of hand"],", if I have found favour in thy sight; and let me not see my wretchedness."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.16","order":"02.05.011.12051"},["b","16"],"¶And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said unto Moses, Gather unto me",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"seventy"],"men of the elders of Israel, whom thou knowest to be the elders of the people, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"officers"],"over them; and bring them unto the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_16c"},"tabernacle of the congregation"],", that they may stand there with thee."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.17","order":"02.05.011.12052"},["b","17"],"And I will come down and talk with thee there: and I will take of the spirit which",["i","is"],"upon thee, and will put",["i","it"],"upon them; and they shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"bear"],"the burden of the people with thee, that thou bear",["i","it"],"not thyself alone."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.18","order":"02.05.011.12053"},["b","18"],"And say thou unto the people, Sanctify yourselves against to morrow, and ye shall eat flesh: for ye have wept in the ears of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", saying, Who shall give us flesh to eat? for",["i","it was"],"well with us in Egypt: therefore the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"will give you flesh, and ye shall eat."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.19","order":"02.05.011.12054"},["b","19"],"Ye shall not eat one day, nor two days, nor five days, neither ten days, nor twenty days;"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.20","order":"02.05.011.12055"},["b","20"],["i","But"],"even a whole month, until it come out at your nostrils, and it be loathsome unto you: because that ye have despised the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"which",["i","is"],"among you, and have wept before him, saying, Why came we forth out of Egypt?"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.21","order":"02.05.011.12056"},["b","21"],"And Moses said, The people, among whom I",["i","am, are"],"six hundred thousand footmen; and thou hast said, I will give them flesh, that they may eat a whole month."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.22","order":"02.05.011.12057"},["b","22"],"Shall the flocks and the herds be slain for them, to suffice them? or shall all the fish of the sea be gathered together for them, to suffice them?"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.23","order":"02.05.011.12058"},["b","23"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said unto Moses, Is the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"’s hand waxed short? thou shalt see now whether my word shall come to pass unto thee or not."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.24","order":"02.05.011.12059"},["b","24"],"¶And Moses went out, and told the people the words of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and gathered the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"seventy"],"men of the elders of the people, and set them round about the tabernacle."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.25","order":"02.05.011.12060"},["b","25"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came down in a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"cloud"],", and spake unto him, and took of the spirit that",["i","was"],"upon him, and gave",["i","it"],"unto the seventy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"elders"],": and it came to pass,",["i","that,"],"when the spirit rested upon them, they",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_25c"},"prophesied"],", and did not cease."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.26","order":"02.05.011.12061"},["b","26"],"But there remained two",["i","of the"],"men in the camp, the name of the one",["i","was"],"Eldad, and the name of the other Medad: and the spirit rested upon them; and they",["i","were"],"of them that were written, but went not out unto the tabernacle: and they prophesied in the camp."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.27","order":"02.05.011.12062"},["b","27"],"And there ran a young man, and told Moses, and said, Eldad and Medad do prophesy in the camp."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.28","order":"02.05.011.12063"},["b","28"],"And",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"Joshua"],"the son of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_28b"},"Nun"],", the servant of Moses,",["i","one"],"of his young men, answered and said, My lord Moses, forbid them."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.29","order":"02.05.011.12064"},["b","29"],"And Moses said unto him, Enviest thou for my sake? would God that all the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"’s people were",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"prophets"],",",["i","and"],"that the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"would put his spirit upon them!"],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.30","order":"02.05.011.12065"},["b","30"],"And Moses gat him into the camp, he and the elders of Israel."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.31","order":"02.05.011.12066"},["b","31"],"¶And there went forth a wind from the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and brought",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"quails"],"from the sea, and let",["i","them"],"fall by the camp, as it were a day’s journey on this side, and as it were a day’s journey on the other side, round about the camp, and as it were two cubits",["i","high"],"upon the face of the earth."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.32","order":"02.05.011.12067"},["b","32"],"And the people stood up all that day, and all",["i","that"],"night, and all the next day, and they gathered the quails: he that gathered least gathered ten homers: and they spread",["i","them"],"all abroad for themselves round about the camp."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.33","order":"02.05.011.12068"},["b","33"],"And while the flesh",["i","was"],"yet between their teeth, ere it was chewed, the wrath of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"was kindled against the people, and the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"smote the people with a very great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_33a"},"plague"],"."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.34","order":"02.05.011.12069"},["b","34"],"And he called the name of that place",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_34a"},"Kibroth-hattaavah"],": because there they buried the people that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_34b"},"lusted"],"."],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.35","order":"02.05.011.12070"},["b","35"],["i","And"],"the people journeyed from Kibroth-hattaavah unto Hazeroth; and abode at Hazeroth."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.1a","order":"02.05.011.12071"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/9.22"},"Deut. 9:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/16.22"},"1 Ne. 16:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/17.2"},"17:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/75.7.7-8"},"D&C 75:7 (7–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.1b","order":"02.05.011.12073"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/32.22"},"Deut. 32:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/78.21"},"Ps. 78:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/15.30"},"1 Ne. 15:30"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/26.6"},"2 Ne. 26:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.14"},"D&C 35:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/128.24"},"128:24"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/7.34"},"Moses 7:34"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.4a","order":"02.05.011.12075"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/lust"},"TG Lust"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.7a","order":"02.05.011.12077"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/16.35"},"Ex. 16:35"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/17.28.15-43"},"1 Ne. 17:28 (15–43)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/7.19"},"Mosiah 7:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.7b","order":"02.05.011.12079"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/16.31"},"Ex. 16:31"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.9a","order":"02.05.011.12081"},["b","9a"],["span.small","OR"],"with it."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.14a","order":"02.05.011.12083"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/18.18"},"Ex. 18:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.15a","order":"02.05.011.12085"},["b","15a"],["span.small","OR"],"immediately."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.16a","order":"02.05.011.12087"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/church-organization"},"TG Church Organization"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/seventy"},"Seventy"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.16b","order":"02.05.011.12089"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/16.18"},"Deut. 16:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.127"},"D&C 88:127"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/107.21"},"107:21"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/delegation-of-responsibility"},"TG Delegation of Responsibility"],"."],["div",{"id":"16c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.16c","order":"02.05.011.12091"},["b","16c"],["span.small","HEB"],"tent of meeting."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.17a","order":"02.05.011.12093"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/leadership"},"TG Leadership"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.24a","order":"02.05.011.12095"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/seventy"},"TG Seventy"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.25a","order":"02.05.011.12097"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/12.5"},"Num. 12:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/2.4.4-5,14"},"Ether 2:4 (4–5, 14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/34.7.7-9"},"D&C 34:7 (7–9)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.68.68-71"},"JS—H 1:68 (68–71)"],"."],["div",{"id":"25b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.25b","order":"02.05.011.12099"},["b","25b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/elder-melchizedek-priesthood"},"TG Elder, Melchizedek Priesthood"],"."],["div",{"id":"25c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.25c","order":"02.05.011.12101"},["b","25c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-gifts-of"},"TG Holy Ghost, Gifts of"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.28a","order":"02.05.011.12103"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/13.16"},"Num. 13:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/7.27"},"1 Chr. 7:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"28b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.28b","order":"02.05.011.12105"},["b","28b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/33.11"},"Ex. 33:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/27.18"},"Num. 27:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/14.1"},"Josh. 14:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/16.34"},"1 Kgs. 16:34"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/neh/8.17"},"Neh. 8:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.29a","order":"02.05.011.12107"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophecy"},"TG Prophecy"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophets-mission-of"},"Prophets, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"31a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.31a","order":"02.05.011.12109"},["b","31a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/16.13"},"Ex. 16:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"33a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.33a","order":"02.05.011.12111"},["b","33a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/plague"},"TG Plague"],"."],["div",{"id":"34a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.34a","order":"02.05.011.12113"},["b","34a"],["span.small","IE"],"The graves of lust."],["div",{"id":"34b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/num/11.34b","order":"02.05.011.12115"},["b","34b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/9.22"},"Deut. 9:22"],"."]]}
